title: Acetate Terrain
name: Acetate Terrain
description:
Acetate is a basemap designed for gorgeous thematic cartography. By providing a neutral basemap you can place additional data on the map that will provide better clarity to the data itself without distracting colors of the basemap.

This Acetate layer includes global terrain hillshading for providing ground context.

The data is from OpenStreetMap and Natural Earth.

Read more about Acetate:  developer.geoiq.com/tools/acetate/

Code is available from: https://github.com/fortiusone/acetate
